,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:44:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>淨係試過一次知</blockquote><br />\n清醒夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係冇控制個夢境 但我知自己發緊夢 都唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你唔知，你只係發緊一個知道自己發緊夢既夢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318fb25fd7c7e78906619f636a62476e6cff733f","tid":331212,"uid":19388,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:55:23.000Z","msg":"有時發夢會醒起 呀 我發緊夢姐<br />\n之後喺夢入面好型咁跳落樓 同飛黎飛去<br />\n但係就永遠都屌唔到閪"},{"pid":"98e1870ff9c4a88dcb436172b93225d6ab0b7c9c","tid":331212,"uid":35408,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:56:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>淨係試過一次知</blockquote><br />\n清醒夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係冇控制個夢境 但我知自己發緊夢 都唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你唔知，你只係發緊一個知道自己發緊夢既夢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實你唔知，上連登只係你發緊一個知道自己上緊連登發夢嘅發緊夢中既夢中夢"},{"pid":"1b7aaaf6d52dc9d9d93cdccf0ffe0d45185d3ea6","tid":331212,"uid":5739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:14:53.000Z","msg":"試過遇到啲好驚既野 之後好似知自己發緊夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就唔驚lu"},{"pid":"558d54789322a37c2bd141d84cf1cc5723c9a1ed","tid":331212,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過夢到啲好驚既野 之後好似知自己發緊夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就唔驚lu</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2975fcd4a8d4fa7e1264ebc1db89b88418bb826f","tid":331212,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>淨係試過一次知</blockquote><br />\n清醒夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係冇控制個夢境 但我知自己發緊夢 都唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你唔知，你只係發緊一個知道自己發緊夢既夢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似有啲道理 <br />\n我好多時知道發緊夢 跟住試下控制夢境嘅時候 <br />\n個夢定唔知我個頭會好似裂開咁 跟住就會醒<br />\n究竟係我道行唔夠 定係個夢真係唔係清醒夢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403df3dd663cd4e794521580de9f46ae4ef96166","tid":331212,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:25:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時發夢會醒起 呀 我發緊夢姐<br />\n之後喺夢入面好型咁跳落樓 同飛黎飛去<br />\n但係就永遠都屌唔到閪</blockquote><br />\n咁撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d976d0664861f0e20986fb90a4b5b485616ba1b","tid":331212,"uid":5760,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:30:07.000Z","msg":"有時會知。通常一知就醒"},{"pid":"c167d6dfac514a448fc15fcacc0197952fc7bca9","tid":331212,"uid":89532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:30:49.000Z","msg":"試過一次發夢醒咗仲係個夢入面 再醒先真醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2391460bdd428c54c5ce6cc4fb4d920032aa69","tid":331212,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:32:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有時發夢會醒起 呀 我發緊夢姐<br />\n之後喺夢入面好型咁跳落樓 同飛黎飛去<br />\n但係就永遠都屌唔到閪</blockquote><br />\n咁撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eee107981e65fb5c52b8248eb38cee2ea61d602","tid":331212,"uid":25659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:35:55.000Z","msg":"我每次發親奇怪/好傷心嘅夢就同自己講<br />\n夢黎咋 唔係真架 快啲醒啦<br />\n<br />\n跟住就會醒咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後好慶幸真係夢而唔係事實"},{"pid":"722a7fb69bbb7a475c6fe07b4549af173ea299d5","tid":331212,"uid":126506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:37:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>淨係試過一次知</blockquote><br />\n清醒夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係冇控制個夢境 但我知自己發緊夢 都唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你唔知，你只係發緊一個知道自己發緊夢既夢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似有啲道理 <br />\n我好多時知道發緊夢 跟住試下控制夢境嘅時候 <br />\n個夢定唔知我個頭會好似裂開咁 跟住就會醒<br />\n究竟係我道行唔夠 定係個夢真係唔係清醒夢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得清醒夢有得訓練 自從第一次玩清醒夢 到而家一星期發一至兩次 不過時間就好短 其實清醒夢係好易醒 所以知道自己發清醒夢既時候一定要冷靜 要慢慢嚟 要等到自己喺夢裏面有觸覺 個夢先會穩定"},{"pid":"61faa9d1cb3ee4013f1bf6b7e9269b70f48988a1","tid":331212,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:39:09.000Z","msg":"試過喺啲好唔合理嘅夢境入面<br />\n會好似張家輝咁講<br />\n「仆你個街夢嚟嘅喂」<br />\n之後就會醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過發過幾次都分唔到真假嘅夢係跌爆咗電話個mon"},{"pid":"24254e47fc0faae59c44bb5665c2e275788f6605","tid":331212,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>淨係試過一次知</blockquote><br />\n清醒夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係冇控制個夢境 但我知自己發緊夢 都唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你唔知，你只係發緊一個知道自己發緊夢既夢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似有啲道理 <br />\n我好多時知道發緊夢 跟住試下控制夢境嘅時候 <br />\n個夢定唔知我個頭會好似裂開咁 跟住就會醒<br />\n究竟係我道行唔夠 定係個夢真係唔係清醒夢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得清醒夢有得訓練 自從第一次玩清醒夢 到而家一星期發一至兩次 不過時間就好短 其實清醒夢係好易醒 所以知道自己發清醒夢既時候一定要冷靜 要慢慢嚟 要等到自己喺夢裏面有觸覺 個夢先會穩定</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我暫時都仲係做到飛嚟飛去同埋月球漫步<br />\n一想轉場或者加條裸女就會醒<br />\n今晚再玩下先"},{"pid":"120382e132150300f8756f5888848b611cb60abb","tid":331212,"uid":126506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:52:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>淨係試過一次知</blockquote><br />\n清醒夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係冇控制個夢境 但我知自己發緊夢 都唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你唔知，你只係發緊一個知道自己發緊夢既夢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似有啲道理 <br />\n我好多時知道發緊夢 跟住試下控制夢境嘅時候 <br />\n個夢定唔知我個頭會好似裂開咁 跟住就會醒<br />\n究竟係我道行唔夠 定係個夢真係唔係清醒夢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得清醒夢有得訓練 自從第一次玩清醒夢 到而家一星期發一至兩次 不過時間就好短 其實清醒夢係好易醒 所以知道自己發清醒夢既時候一定要冷靜 要慢慢嚟 要等到自己喺夢裏面有觸覺 個夢先會穩定</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我暫時都仲係做到飛嚟飛