e>淨係試過一次知</blockquote><br />\n清醒夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係冇控制個夢境 但我知自己發緊夢 都唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你唔知，你只係發緊一個知道自己發緊夢既夢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似有啲道理 <br />\n我好多時知道發緊夢 跟住試下控制夢境嘅時候 <br />\n個夢定唔知我個頭會好似裂開咁 跟住就會醒<br />\n究竟係我道行唔夠 定係個夢真係唔係清醒夢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得清醒夢有得訓練 自從第一次玩清醒夢 到而家一星期發一至兩次 不過時間就好短 其實清醒夢係好易醒 所以知道自己發清醒夢既時候一定要冷靜 要慢慢嚟 要等到自己喺夢裏面有觸覺 個夢先會穩定</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我暫時都仲係做到飛嚟飛去同埋月球漫步<br />\n一想轉場或者加條裸女就會醒<br />\n今晚再玩下先</blockquote><br />\n發到既時候feel下自己隻手 睇下有無觸覺先 無既話就等到有feel先玩 會玩耐好多 btw我未去過月球 你飛上去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係 係喺個夢入面好似喺月球咁 行一步好似跳咁 彈到好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又係同巴打一樣試過夢裂開就醒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想玩耐啲</blockquote><br />\n學上面巴打話齋 唔好太急進<br />\n我今晚試下 有觸覺先開始玩<br />\n不過要知自己發夢 其實唔係咁易 都唔係日日有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aca1e50577ba3e91e0e2ee3470e0416c7b164db","tid":331212,"uid":34440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:02:00.000Z","msg":"我試過發夢唔知點解飛緊<br />\n之後向下跌 我諗住升返上去就真係升返上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d96b30b6aac0d199376fb0f1038da2206613c96","tid":331212,"uid":86942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"清醒夢係有得練 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好耐以前都只係可以係原地周圍望 想行去第個位就會醒<br />\n後來有一次係諗移動唔得 咁訓係度都得掛 跟住向後一唉落去就突然明左夢入面移動原來要好似打機fly mode咁樣去控制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a573a13ddbac7dd486b183ee64d50a5e10ce1577","tid":331212,"uid":59901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:13:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唯一一個知自己係發緊夢既timing就係無啦啦好急要去搵廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔醒就賴尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9546c71072f4422a2b0302c8972311dd5199856","tid":331212,"uid":64847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:13:42.000Z","msg":"試過兩次<br />\n其中一次控制自己跳海 （個陣唔識游水）<br />\n跟住就醒咗"},{"pid":"ea055ce0196643917d141c2fb7960425ecbca3ed","tid":331212,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:21:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清醒夢係有得練 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好耐以前都只係可以係原地周圍望 想行去第個位就會醒<br />\n後來有一次係諗移動唔得 咁訓係度都得掛 跟住向後一唉落去就突然明左夢入面移動原來要好似打機fly mode咁樣去控制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁巴打而家去到邊個level? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c408c4d9044b092257a8a767adf2dc59676181cd","tid":331212,"uid":23046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T07:13:19.000Z","msg":"有練過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家荒廢左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾好玩<br />\n練到去控制/創造到小小物件or事<br />\n例：飛/召喚物件/控制人或者即將發生既事<br />\n<br />\n練左一陣就已經可以控制到身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22424f106fc30405d4bdea745ca67d28c2f31830","tid":331212,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T07:14:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有練過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla